Hey! What's going on with those poorly made copycats?
Oh shut it! They are driving me crazy!
Don't underestimate this enemy
Arrogance kills curiosity and passion. They are dead to us.
Don't get too close
model: or there would be a counterattack.

monster_desc: We do not train to be merciful here. Go get 'em!
Careful
It seems very difficult to anticipate their next move. Let's see how it goes for a while.
Horrifying enemies that carry out suicidal attacks. Defend yourselves.
Significant enhancement in the combat power.
Can't imagine what it would be like if one day the heroes turn against us.
Look at what they did to us!! A real pain in the neck.
Let us put an end to this.
Impatient and easily irritated. Never interrupt your enemy when he is making a mistake.
Don't ever show mercy upon your enemies
They have thoughts
model: emotions. Wonder how things will go from there.
